# 安装

```bash
dotnet add package Watermark.Net
```

```powershell
Install-Package Watermark.Net
```

要求：

- .NET 8 或更高版本

---

# 快速开始

## 添加文字水印

```csharp
var watermark = new TextWatermark
{
    Text = "CONFIDENTIAL",
    Font = SystemFonts.CreateFont("Arial", 36)
};
```

---

## 添加图片水印

```csharp
var watermark = new ImageWatermark
{
    ImagePath = "logo.png"
};
```

